Ylva watched the exchange with interest, then clapped Davinia on the shoulder. "Good. I joined you because you killed a dragon. But I'll stay because you remembered you're still human."
She grinned at Alfonso. "Even if some of you technically aren't."

PART III: THE SIEGE OF KORVANJUND
